</a>
<div class='talk-speaker__details media__message'>
<div class='talk-speaker__name h10'>
<a class="l3 talk-speaker__link" href="/speakers/mark_pagel">Mark Pagel</a>
</div>
<div class='talk-speaker__description'>
Evolutionary biologist
</div>
<div class='talk-speaker__bio'>
Using biological evolution as a template, Mark Pagel wonders how languages evolve.
<a class="l3 talk-speaker__link" href="/speakers/mark_pagel">Full bio</a>
</div>
